Class BasePropertySequence

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.data.gcd.BasePropertySequence
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, PropertySequence
public class BasePropertySequence
extends Object
implements PropertySequence, Cloneable

A default implementation of the PropertySequence interface. Internally a sequence of (name, value) properties is represented with two java.lang.ArrayList containers holding respectively names and values. Thus, calling the removeProperty method instantaneously changes the number of properties returned by getCount().
